    "name": "ONI：鬼族武者立志传",
    "steam_appid": 2101190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/7a62d51e399d7b82f01ca5a545293ddf.avif?t=1741319385\" width=616 height=89 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜关于本作＞</h2><strong>■由五位核心成员携手打造的“小小世界游戏”</strong><br>在以KENEI DESIGN团队为核心，由五位创作者花费两年时间打造的“鬼世岛”当中，<br>玩家可以体验到宛如掉入孩提时代看过的绘本般世界的感受。<br>鬼世岛作为游玩的地图来说虽然并不大，但举凡玩家接触到的世界观、角色到音乐等元素，都充满了创作者们的坚持。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/ONI5.GIF?t=1741319385\" /></span><br><br><strong>■完成任务型的动作游戏</strong><br>在这座小岛上，小鬼“空太”将必须接受考验。碰触鬼世岛各地的鬼族幻影，便会前往考验专用的关卡。依序完成考验，除了可推进游戏进度外，也能使空太有所成长。敬请享受有别于探索广大地图的开放世界的体验，专属于完成任务型动作游戏的乐趣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/3580283ed2f9630c152fea997d7d03dd.poster.avif?t=1741319385\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/3580283ed2f9630c152fea997d7d03dd.webm?t=1741319385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/3580283ed2f9630c152fea997d7d03dd.mp4?t=1741319385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>■独一无二的特殊动作元素！</strong><br>主角空太能手握棍棒发动多样化的攻击，对身为“意念体”的敌人造成伤害。而搭档风丸则能与敌人拉开距离，从远处抽出他们的“心”。玩家同时操作空太与风丸时，将能享受到前所未有的“一心同体”动作乐趣！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/ONI1.GIF?t=1741319385\" /></span><br><br><strong>■简直就像捉迷藏！？独树一格的成长要素</strong><br>游戏舞台“鬼世岛”可分为三个地区，其中安排了从仅只是打倒敌人到保护支援角色等各式各样的考验。其他还有逃离神出鬼没的妖怪追杀以增强体力、搜集群生蘑菇以购买新的棍棒等要素，可以享受逐渐变强的乐趣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/ONI2.GIF?t=1741319385\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/b9bf3b47d1937f4d146d7d0c02c46cf3.avif?t=1741319385\" width=616 height=89 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜ONI：鬼族武士立志传 游戏简介＞</h2><strong>■故事的舞台：小巧的孤岛“鬼世岛”</strong><br>本作的舞台“鬼世岛”是四面都被海峡环绕的渺小孤岛。传说在这座岛上唤醒从前被桃太郎打败的鬼族们的意念并与它们战斗接受“考验”，即可唤醒沉睡在鬼族体内的力量。然而，至今从未有挑战者从岛上活着回来过。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/ONI3.GIF?t=1741319385\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/a23640c14cf7658544e4b05ee16254f1.avif?t=1741319385\" width=616 height=89 /></span><br><strong>■角色：鬼族战士“空太”和精灵搭档“风丸”</strong><br>主角“空太”是挑战桃太郎的鬼王军当中唯一幸存的战士。他将和栖息在鬼世岛上的奇妙精灵“风丸”一起接受各式各样的考验！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/ONI4.GIF?t=1741319385\" /></span><br><br><strong>■角色：神秘少女“叶渚”</strong><br>“鬼世岛”上一位温柔而神秘的少女。在因缘际会下遇见为了接受考验而来到岛上的空太，逐渐和他彼此熟识。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/0ad7d9da9007aedc41cf7cdcf9b1de99.avif?t=1741319385\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>■角色：“猪宝”</strong><br>栖息在“鬼世岛”上的山猪的孩子。主要以菇类为食，过着自由自在的生活。只要空太叫唤便会立刻赶去，载着他奔驰在岛上各地。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101190/extras/e18a62c6ffb5c24296ab6f96728b7656.avif?t=1741319385\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
